Knowledgeable Technical Writer with a strong background in the computer software industry, adept at creating comprehensive documentation and enhancing user experiences. Skilled in Microsoft Word, HTML, CSS, Madcap Flare, Adobe Technical Communication Suite, and Camtasia for video editing. Experience in authoring and publishing help content using Zendesk Guide and developing content for generative AI features. Demonstrated expertise in crafting interactive tours and a strong interest in UX writing. A dedicated, life-long learner, seeking to continuously refine skills and stay updated with industry trends. Holds a Bachelor of Arts in English with concentrations in Creative Writing and a Minor in Communication Studies from Huntingdon College.
